        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De conscientia benignitatis et malignitatis</head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e114">
           De conscientia 
           <lb ed="#O"/>benignitatis et malignitatis. ¶ Rubrica. 3
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e121">
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e118">ORatius epistolarum libro 1. e. 1.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e127">hic 
           <lb ed="#O"/>murus eneus extat. Nil 
           <lb ed="#O"/>conscii sibi nulla pallescere culpa.</quote> 
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e134">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e135">TUllius de senectute</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e138">Conscientia 
           bene acte uite multorumque bene<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ficiorum 
           recordatio iocundissima est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e147"> 
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e148">Idem tuscalanarum que stionum libro 2.</ref> ¶ 
           <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e149">Nullum theatrum uirtute et conscientia 
           <lb ed="#O"/>maius est.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e157">
           <!--line bumps down-->
           <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e163">OUidius <!--line bumps up--> de fastis libro 1.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e161">Conscientia <!--line bumps back down--> mens ut cuique sua est 
           <lb ed="#O"/>sic concipit intra ¶ Pectore pro<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>fecto 
           spemque metumque suo.</quote>
        </p>
        <!--LEFT OFF HERE-->
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e169"> 
           ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e175">libro 4</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e171">
           Conscia mens recti fame mendacia ridet.
           Sed nos in uitium credula turba sumus.</quote>
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e186">¶ Seneca in prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e188">Plerique famam conscien
           tiam pauci uerentur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e183">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e198">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola. 2. ad corinth. capitulo 1.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e187">Gloria
           nostra hoc est testimonium conscientie nostre.</quote>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e206">¶ Statius thebandos libro 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e208">O sper timidum scelus</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e195">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e215">¶ Iuuenalis libro 2. satis 1.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e199">Cui frigida mens est
           Criminibus tacita sudant praecordia culpa.</quote>
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e224">¶ Marcialis cocus l. vndique suscepto. capitulo 6.</ref>
           <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e229">Ibis ad occultos tramites loca deuia mundi
           Peccatum tecum est conscientie culpa comes.
           Alterius censor censor et esto tuus.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e213">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e241">¶ Ambrosius de officiis li. 2. capitulo 1.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e217">Uitam 
           beatam efficiunt tranquillitas conscientie et 
           securitas innocentie. </quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e232">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e262">¶ Augustinus in epig. prospe. 8. emp.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e236">
           Bona conscientia tranquillum facit animu.</quote>
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e271">Macrobius de somno scipionis libro 2. et fi.</ref>
           <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e276">Uirtutis fructum sapiens in conscientia ponit
           minus perfctus in gloria.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e248">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e286">¶ Cato. capitulo 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e252">Conscius ipse sibi de se putat
           omnia dici.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e258">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e298">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum libro 7. capitulo 32.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e262">Totum ui
           tiosum geritur ubi conscientie puritas non habetur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e270"> 
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e310">libro 8. e. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e272">Sicut conscientia leta est
           que prouehitur meritis ita sub reatu iacet
           qui se imparem cognoscit muneribus 
           consecutis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e282"> 
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e324">libro 11. capitulo 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e284">Quid acquiri 
           putatur ubi conscientia bona perditur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e290">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e336">¶ Isidorus soliloquiorum libro 2. capitulo 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e294">Deus 
           conscientias iudicat.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e301"> 
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e347">capitulo 37.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e303">Etsi non te damnet
           publica fama condennat propria conscia.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e309"> 
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e357">capitulo 38</ref>
           <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e311">Conscientia rei semper tin pena est. Mens
           male conscientie propriis agitatur stimulis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e319">
           <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Rd1e371">¶ Prouerb. uulgar.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e323">Lamore guasta la conscia</quote>
        </p>
      </div>
